, \u201cIt is that you are grateful in prosperity and patient in adversity. If one is like that, he is temperate.\u201d It was said, \u201cWhat is\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33755,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/11\/10\/sufyan-dua-hardship\/","url_meta":{"origin":9887,"position":4},"title":"Sufyan on Dua: Hardship with supplication better than ease","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 10, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Ruh reported: Sufyan ibn \u2018Uyaynah, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cWhat a servant dislikes is better for him than what he likes, as what he dislikes compels him to supplicate and what he likes distracts him from it.\u201d Source: al-Faraj ba\u2019d al-Shiddah 21 \u0639\u0646 \u0623\u0628\u064a \u0631\u064e\u0648\u0652\u062d\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":22296,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/03\/24\/sufyan-dislikes-good-dua\/","url_meta":{"origin":9887,"position":5},"title":"Sufyan on Dua: What he dislikes is good if he prays about it","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 24, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abi Dunya reported: Sufyan ibn 'Uyaynah, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cWhat a servant dislikes may be better for him than what he likes. What he dislikes inspires him to supplicate to Allah, and what he 